@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_thgyyl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.77)) / 0.74)
    v2 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.74) / 0.71) * wp.cos((v2 + 0.51 / v1 + 0.93)))
    tmp = (0.30 / ((v2 + 0.94 / tmp + 0.27) * (v0 + 0.88 / tmp + 0.36)))
    v1 = 0.80
    v1 = tmp
    v0 = v0
    v1 = v1
    data[tid] = v0
